snippet.title: Beast Mode: Night Of The Werewolf Silver Bullet Edition - Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Beast Mode: Night of the Werewolf has been remastered into the new Silver Bullet Edition! Join the Playtest starting September 29th, 2023: https://store.steampowered.com/app/655760/
Music: Battleground by: Ethan Meixsell.
